This week's deal was played by Norway's ^*BGeir Helgemo^*N during the recent ^*BGenerali World Masters Individual^*N in Athens, Greece. Full coverage of the Generali, including ^*BOnline Vugraph^*N, is available through:

|cs|1|at|^-{ ^*Bwww.bridgeplaza.com^*N }
